flowchart LR
  A[Bad answer] --> B[Collect trace]
  B --> C[Inspect chunks, scores, filters]
  C --> D[Compare with gold evidence]
  D --> E[Label failure]
  E --> F[Test one controlled fix]
  F --> G[Run golden queries]
  G --> H{Pass release gate?}
  H -->|Yes| I[Release]
  H -->|No| J[Rollback or keep investigating]
